description:
Doug gives his thoughts on the horror football film from producer Jordan Peel. Is it the touchdown they hope it'll be? Let's take a look at Him (2025).

Check out our store - https://channelawesome.myshopify.com/

Him is a 2025 American supernatural psychological sports horror film directed by Justin Tipping, co-written by Skip Bronkie, Zack Akers, and Tipping, and produced by Jordan Peele's Monkeypaw Productions. The film stars Marlon Wayans, Tyriq Withers, Julia Fox, Tim Heidecker, and Jim Jefferies. Its plot follows the trials of a young up-and-coming football player training at the isolated compound of an aging, nearly retired quarterback.
